---
title: Posh Pork Sausage Subs with Caramelised Pear & Fries
description: We're taking subs into dinner territory with this hearty recipe using juicy pork sausages. Sandwiched in warm crusty ciabatta rolls and topped with mustard mayo, rocket and caramelised pear and onion, they're just the thing for a casual dinner that's still a bit fancy.
